WEBVTT

1
00:49:04.380 --> 00:49:07.650 
但至少在想象中
it was possible, in the mind's eye at least,

2
00:49:07.980 --> 00:49:10.770 
朝西向着落日
to gaze west towards the setting sun

3
00:49:11.000 --> 00:49:14.150 
有可能看到清晰的伊甸园
and see an unclouded Eden.

4
00:49:15.990 --> 00:49:18.760 
一些华丽的全景画由此诞生
Some truly lurid panorama paintings

5
00:49:18.760 --> 00:49:22.420 
代表了天堂的幻想
were produced in the name of these paradise illusions,

6
00:49:19.070 --> 00:49:24.500 
弗雷德里克·艾德温·丘奇《荒野曙光》(1860)

7
00:49:22.630 --> 00:49:26.710 
都在天意之光的照耀下熠熠生辉
all shining with the stage lighting of Providence.

8
00:49:28.480 --> 00:49:31.480 
令人伤感的是  和大多数传道一样
All of these efforts, like most propaganda,

9
00:49:31.590 --> 00:49:36.920 
托马斯·莫兰《山景》(1865)

10
00:49:31.640 --> 00:49:35.330 
所有这些一旦战争结束就被遗忘
were sentimentally forgettable once the war was over.

